BioScCc

The undirected graph BioScCc has 2223 nodes and 34879 edges.

RAM requirements

The nodes with highest degree centrality are: 1 (degree 571 and weighted degree 571), 4 (degree 549 and weighted degree 549), 15 (degree 466 and weighted degree 466), 36 (degree 408 and weighted degree 408) and 248 (degree 370 and weighted degree 370).

Weights
